                                    <condition>The manuscript has been rebound and the edges trimmed. In the process of rebinding, the bifolium making up <locus from="164" to="164" scheme="folios"/>/<locus from="174" to="174" scheme="folios"/> has been misplaced; this bifolium should follow after <locus from="163" to="163" scheme="folios"/>/<locus from="175" to="175" scheme="folios"/>. Several edges and corners have been repaired with paper strips. Half of <locus from="144" to="144" scheme="folios"/> has been torn off; the missing half has been replaced with a paper strip.</condition>
